data.description: Charming 2 bedroom/1 bath Cottage on .48 acres located in a quiet country neighborhood between Center Point and Comfort. The Log and Chink entry invites you into the foyer with a wall of windows. Hardwood and Saltillo floors, large primary bedroom and the open concept add to the character of this quaint home. The peaceful covered front porch is perfect for enjoying your morning coffee. Recent upgrades include appliances, roof, interior and exterior paint, back deck, electrical, plumbing, insulation, water heater, and 2 new mini splits. Other features include a workshop with attached carport and a storage building and a new greenhouse. A variety of hardwoods adorn the property with nicely landscaped beds. This diverse property offers numerous possibilities.
